descriptionHtml:
My New Elven Dagger texture...

Instal.:

- copy the texture folder to your Data folder (...Skyrim/Data/...)

- if textures allready exist, copy the weapons folder to textures (...Skyrim/Data/textures/...)

- if weapons folder allready exist, copy the elven folder to weapons 
  (...Skyrim/Data/textures/weapons/...)

- if elven folder allready exist, copy the dagger folder to elven 
  (...Skyrim/Data/textures/weapons/elven/...)
author: Seycho
